data.text: @MasterPancake @TheMadsAreBack I don't suppose Quincy and Baywatch was a two part crossover episode. I want to live in a world where such a thing exists.

@MasterPancake @TheMadsAreBack From the guy who brought you the UNSOLVED MYSTERY about the Immortal Mummy of John Wilkes Booth (the world's most handsome & talented actor), it's 1991's DISNEY PRESENTS THE 100 LIVES OF BLACK JACK SAVAGE -- a rich man & a 17th-century pirate ghost start a detective agency. https://t.co/E3tKB0m0LE
